285
00:41:24,972 --> 00:41:26,963
Jos nisi vidjela sve.

286
00:41:27,074 --> 00:41:28,803
Vec mi se svidja.

287
00:41:30,678 --> 00:41:32,339
Pazi ovdje.

288
00:41:32,747 --> 00:41:34,271
Sve je trulo.

289
00:41:36,217 --> 00:41:38,048
Masinska soba.

290
00:41:45,893 --> 00:41:47,224
Gore.

291
00:41:51,932 --> 00:41:53,331
Sacekaj trenutak.

292
00:41:58,539 --> 00:42:00,029
Cekaj.Pusti me prvoga..

293
00:42:13,054 --> 00:42:17,252
Za nas ugovor!
Molim vas udjite, gospodo.

294
00:42:27,301 --> 00:42:33,672
Sada kada je prodaja broda zavrsena,
bicu sasvim iskren.

295
00:42:33,941 --> 00:42:34,930
Bolje ti je.

296
00:42:35,042 --> 00:42:40,036
Primorao sam te da uzmes Choloa kao mehanicara
ili ne bi imao brod

297
00:42:42,583 --> 00:42:44,141
Shvatam to.

298
00:42:44,452 --> 00:42:47,114
Vrlo dobro.Dobro.

299
00:42:47,221 --> 00:42:51,419
On je prvoklasni mehanicar,
to je sve sto cu ti reci.

300
00:42:55,396 --> 00:42:57,023
A sta jos je on?

301
00:42:57,131 --> 00:43:00,623
Razlog koji se krije iza svega toga ,
izvini moj bezobrazluk,. . .

302
00:43:00,735 --> 00:43:05,229
. . .da ja zelim biti informisan
o aktivnostima mogkonkurenta.

303
00:43:05,339 --> 00:43:09,833
Ne zelim da mi moji poslovi budu oduzeti.

304
00:43:10,478 --> 00:43:12,036
Ne brini.

305
00:43:13,047 --> 00:43:15,607
Svaki vlasnik parobroda je
potencijalni neprijatelj. . .

306
00:43:15,716 --> 00:43:19,652
. . .ali ovi koji imaju samo kanue
ne mogu nas povrijediti.

307
00:43:21,922 --> 00:43:24,447
Nas dvojica mozemo se kladiti. . .

308
00:43:24,558 --> 00:43:27,220
. . .koliko dugo ce proci
prije nego sto bankrotiras.

309
00:43:27,328 --> 00:43:30,161
O, ne uzimaj to licno, molim te.

310
00:43:30,264 --> 00:43:32,960
Mi smo svi sportisti, nismo li ?

311
00:43:34,468 --> 00:43:36,402
Ne, samo jedan od nas.

312
00:43:38,372 --> 00:43:40,306
Ja treba da pomaknem planinu.

313
00:44:21,949 --> 00:44:23,917
Kada ce ona biti spremna?

314
00:44:27,388 --> 00:44:30,221
Sutra. Vec cetiri dana mi govori
sutra.

315
00:44:30,324 --> 00:44:32,417
Nadam se da ce biti spremna za porinuce.

316
00:44:37,198 --> 00:44:40,793
Pitam se sta ovaj lik
zaista planira.

317
00:45:25,312 --> 00:45:26,370
Kako se zoves?

318
00:45:26,480 --> 00:45:29,381
Paul Resenbrink. Holandjanin sam.

319
00:45:30,351 --> 00:45:32,285
Oni me zovu Orinoco Paul. . .

320
00:45:33,053 --> 00:45:36,113
. . .Zato sto poznajem svaku prokletu
krivinu ove rijeke.

321
00:45:38,993 --> 00:45:41,154
Nisi plovio neko vrijeme.

322
00:45:41,929 --> 00:45:44,830
To je tacno.
Moj posljednji brod bio je  Adolfo.

323
00:45:45,032 --> 00:45:48,593
Moj vid nije dobar,
ali ne mozes me prevariti.

324
00:45:49,837 --> 00:45:51,236
Kako to mislis?

325
00:45:51,338 --> 00:45:54,068
Dzungla pravi trikove sa tvojim culima.

326
00:45:54,174 --> 00:45:57,666
Puna je lazi, demona, iluzija.

327
00:45:58,145 --> 00:46:03,412
Naucio sam da kazem razliku
izmedju realnosti i iluzija.

328
00:46:05,619 --> 00:46:09,646
Vidim da si ucestvovao
u Pachitea ekspediciji, 1886.

329
00:46:09,723 --> 00:46:11,418
Da kao kormilar.

330
00:46:11,692 --> 00:46:14,126
Na putu nazad, ja sam bio kapetan..

331
00:46:14,628 --> 00:46:18,792
Kapetan je umro.
Bilo je samo nekoliko prezivjelih.

332
00:46:22,303 --> 00:46:25,500
Paul Resenbrink, imas
posao kapetana.

333
00:46:25,606 --> 00:46:27,699
Pomozi mi da nadjem posadu.

334
00:46:29,043 --> 00:46:31,671
Trebamo jake, neustrasive ljude.

335
00:46:32,046 --> 00:46:35,140
Bojim se da cemo naci svega par dobrih ljudi ovdje.

336
00:46:35,282 --> 00:46:37,375
Prvo, trebamo pilota.

337
00:46:40,321 --> 00:46:43,222
Da li iko ima
iskustva kao pilot ?

338
00:46:49,596 --> 00:46:53,828
Bjezi, ti krzljavko!
Ja sam Huerequeque.

339
00:47:00,341 --> 00:47:04,505
Brethren! I am Huerequeque!

340
00:47:04,979 --> 00:47:07,607
Ja sam najbolji kuvar u citavom
el Amazonas.

341
00:47:07,748 --> 00:47:11,206
Bio sam na svakom brodu.

342
00:47:11,652 --> 00:47:17,386
I amigo, ja nisam glup.
Ja znam sta su vasi planovi.

343
00:47:17,891 --> 00:47:21,258
Huerequeque may tip the bottle
now and then. . .

344
00:47:22,029 --> 00:47:26,898
. . .but up here. . .electric, electrico!

345
00:47:30,137 --> 00:47:35,837
Takodje ja sam najbolji strijelac
na cijelom  Amazonu.

346
00:47:35,943 --> 00:47:39,379
- Sta mislis o njemu?
- Uzvodno i nizvodno.

347
00:47:39,613 --> 00:47:42,446
- Je li on stvarno dobar strijelac?
- Morao bih reci,da.

348
00:47:43,450 --> 00:47:45,179
Kako bjese tvoje ime? Huere. . .

349
00:47:45,285 --> 00:47:46,752
Huerequeque.

350
00:47:50,591 --> 00:47:53,389
Huerequeque, ti si nas kuvar.

351
00:47:53,694 --> 00:47:55,662
Zivjeli, onda.

352
00:48:02,236 --> 00:48:03,294
Molim te shvati.

353
00:48:03,404 --> 00:48:06,999
Ko je kupio brod?
Ko placa za posadu?

354
00:48:07,107 --> 00:48:08,768
Moje je pravo da podjem sa tobom.

355
00:48:08,876 --> 00:48:13,370
Molly,ne mozes ostaviti djevojke.
Sta ce one raditi bez tebe?

356
00:48:13,547 --> 00:48:15,674
A sta cu ja raditi bez tebe?

357
00:48:15,783 --> 00:48:17,478
Vraticu se.

358
00:48:19,620 --> 00:48:22,714
Fitz. . .da li me jos uvijek volis?

359
00:48:24,191 --> 00:48:26,352
Mi smo partneri, ti i ja.

360
00:49:22,783 --> 00:49:26,947
O Fitz, ti si lud!

361
00:50:17,237 --> 00:50:21,173
O Fitz, divno je!

362
00:50:21,275 --> 00:50:23,266
Ovo je tvoj dan, Molly!

363
00:50:32,286 --> 00:50:34,345
Dao si brodu moje ime!

364
00:50:34,621 --> 00:50:37,818
to je vise od onoga sto moje
jadno srce moze da podnese.

365
00:50:37,958 --> 00:50:39,858
sada dolazi oficijalni dio.

366
00:50:40,260 --> 00:50:43,821
Evo. baci-- jako!

367
00:51:07,054 --> 00:51:09,147
Ne zeliom ove seÒoritas
na palubi mog broda.

368
00:51:09,256 --> 00:51:13,158
Ovo su moji asistenti.
