369
00:51:13,260 --> 00:51:15,421
Ajde, djeco, ajde.

370
00:52:03,343 --> 00:52:05,607
Zasto on ne ide dole do Ucayali?

371
00:52:06,647 --> 00:52:08,706
Zasto on plovi uzvodno?

372
00:52:08,815 --> 00:52:11,249
Mislio sam da on ide
do Pongo das Mortes.

373
00:52:11,351 --> 00:52:12,716
Dobro si vidio.

374
00:52:12,819 --> 00:52:16,118
Brian Sweeney Fitzgerald
ide gore uz  Amazon.

375
00:53:07,641 --> 00:53:10,735
Plovimo uzvodno!
Kakva li je ideja?

376
00:53:11,244 --> 00:53:14,338
